PN,41801
SC,0001
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F418A1784211519
OL,3,CLegal challenge over 1994 Chinook
OL,4,Ccrash should continue, High Court told
OL,6,FA legal challenge against the Ministry
OL,7,Fof Defence (MOD) over the 1994 RAF
OL,8,FChinook helicopter crash should be
OL,9,Fallowed to proceed, the High Court has
OL,10,Fbeen told, amid concerns over the
OL,11,Fairworthiness of the aircraft.
OL,13,FTen high ranking RUC officers from
OL,14,FNorthern Ireland were among 29 people
OL,15,Fkilled when the helicopter carrying
OL,16,Fsecurity personnel to a conference in
OL,17,FScotland came down on the Mull of
OL,18,FKintyre. A 2011 inquiry concluding
OL,19,Fthat an initial decision to blame the
OL,20,Fpilots was incorrect.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G1/12
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
