OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,419,410,140,120,000,100
PN,41802
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F418A1784211519
OL,3,CLegal challenge over 1994 Chinook
OL,4,Ccrash should continue, High Court told
OL,6,FThe Chinook Justice Campaign (CJC),
OL,7,Fwhich is made up of more than 55
OL,8,Ffamily members of 25 of the victims,
OL,9,Fis now seeking to challenge the MOD's
OL,10,F"ongoing failure" to set up an
OL,11,F"independent and effective
OL,12,Finvestigation" into the crash, which
OL,13,Fit says breaches human rights.
OL,26,@rD@AOUrD@QO]sD@AOUtD@NO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G2/12
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,419,410,140,120,000,100
PN,41803
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F418A1784211519
OL,3,CLegal challenge over 1994 Chinook
OL,4,Ccrash should continue, High Court told
OL,6,FLawyers for the group told the High
OL,7,FCourt on Tuesday that information
OL,8,Fregarding the Chinook's airworthiness
OL,9,F"raises a more than arguable claim
OL,10,Fthat... those individuals who died in
OL,11,Fthe crash were placed on an aircraft
OL,12,Fknown to be unsafe", and that the
OL,13,Flegal claim should be allowed to
OL,14,Fproceed.
OL,16,FThe MOD is defending the legal bid,
OL,17,Fwith its barristers telling the court
OL,18,Fthat the claim has been brought too
OL,19,Flate and that human rights have not
OL,20,Fbeen breached.
OL,26,@qD@AOUtD@SO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G3/12
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,419,410,140,120,000,100
PN,41804
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F418A1784211519
OL,3,CLegal challenge over 1994 Chinook
OL,4,Ccrash should continue, High Court told
OL,6,FSam Jacobs, for the CJC, told the
OL,7,Fcourt in London that there were
OL,8,F"profound and stark" concerns as to
OL,9,Fairworthiness, but that no
OL,10,Finvestigation had ever considered the
OL,11,Fissue despite several probes into the
OL,12,Fcrash.
OL,14,FHe said: "It is historic, but it is
OL,15,Falso extraordinary, that the bereaved
OL,16,Ffamilies of 29 individuals... still
OL,17,Fface unanswered questions into the
OL,18,Fcircumstances of what is often
OL,19,Fdescribed as the RAF's worst peacetime
OL,20,Fdisaster."
OL,26,@pD@AOUpD@TO]vD@JOU|D@JO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G4/12
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,419,410,140,120,000,100
PN,41805
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F418A1784211519
OL,3,CLegal challenge over 1994 Chinook
OL,4,Ccrash should continue, High Court told
OL,6,FHe continued: "What the bereaved
OL,7,Ffamilies want is candour from the MOD
OL,8,Fabout what the MOD does know about
OL,9,Fwhat opportunities it appears may have
OL,10,Fexisted to avoid such a major loss of
OL,11,Flife."
OL,13,FSpeaking outside the Royal Courts of
OL,14,FJustice on Tuesday, Andy Tobias, whose
OL,15,Ffather Lieutenant Colonel John Tobias
OL,16,FMBE died in the crash, said it was a
OL,17,F"hugely momentous day".
OL,19,FSeveral relatives of those who died
OL,20,Fattended court, some of whom wept
OL,21,Fduring the hearing.
OL,26,@nD@OOUsD@FO]yD@AOUyD@VO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G5/12
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,419,410,140,120,000,100
PN,41806
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F418A1784211519
OL,3,CLegal challenge over 1994 Chinook
OL,4,Ccrash should continue, High Court told
OL,6,FThe helicopter was transporting 25
OL,7,Fintelligence experts and four special
OL,8,Fforces crew from RAF Aldergrove in
OL,9,FNorthern Ireland to Fort George near
OL,10,FInverness when it crashed in foggy
OL,11,Fweather.
OL,13,FIn written submissions, Mr Jacobs said
OL,14,Fthat the crash came two days after the
OL,15,Fhelicopter was delivered, following a
OL,16,F"fraught upgrade and introduction".
OL,26,@xD@AOUxD@bO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G6/12
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,419,410,140,120,000,100
PN,41807
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F418A1784211519
OL,3,CLegal challenge over 1994 Chinook
OL,4,Ccrash should continue, High Court told
OL,6,FHe continued that the MOD was suing
OL,7,FBoeing over the upgrade before the
OL,8,Fcrash, and that a safety-critical
OL,9,Fengine control system on the
OL,10,Fhelicopter was described by the
OL,11,FAircraft and Armament Experimental
OL,12,FEstablishment as having a "density of
OL,13,Fdeficiencies".
OL,15,FMr Jacobs also said that the
OL,16,Fhelicopter involved in the crash
OL,17,Fneeded one of its engines replaced
OL,18,Fthree times in the months before the
OL,19,Fincident, with issues also reported
OL,20,Fwith its second engine.
OL,26,@tD@[OUuD@MO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G7/12
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,419,410,140,120,000,100
PN,41808
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F418A1784211519
OL,3,CLegal challenge over 1994 Chinook
OL,4,Ccrash should continue, High Court told
OL,6,FHe said: "It is plainly arguable that
OL,7,Fairworthiness caused the crash;
OL,8,Findeed, arguable that the HC-2 should
OL,9,Fnot have been flying at all."
OL,11,FHe continued: "There is nothing before
OL,12,Fthe court to indicate that the
OL,13,Fimperative to deploy the HC-2, at that
OL,14,Ftime, was so severe, and the concerns
OL,15,Fas to airworthiness sufficiently
OL,16,Fmitigated, that the decision to deploy
OL,17,Fis immune from reasonable criticism."
OL,26,@nD@JOUqD@]O]sD@OOUyD@eO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G8/12
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,419,410,140,120,000,100
PN,41809
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F418A1784211519
OL,3,CLegal challenge over 1994 Chinook
OL,4,Ccrash should continue, High Court told
OL,6,FThe incident was first investigated by
OL,7,Fan internal Board of Inquiry in 1995,
OL,8,Fwhich concluded that there was an
OL,9,Ferror on the part of the pilots,
OL,10,FFlight Lieutenants Jonathan Tapper and
OL,11,FRichard Cook.
OL,13,FA Scottish Fatal Accident Inquiry and
OL,14,Fthe House of Commons Public Accounts
OL,15,FCommittee both reached different
OL,16,Fconclusions, with the Board of
OL,17,FInquiry's findings overturned
OL,18,Ffollowing the 2011 review, although
OL,19,Fthis did not determine the cause of
OL,20,Fthe crash.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G9/12
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,419,410,140,120,000,100
PN,41810
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F418A1784211519
OL,3,CLegal challenge over 1994 Chinook
OL,4,Ccrash should continue, High Court told
OL,6,FDaniel Beard KC, for the MOD, said in
OL,7,Fwritten submissions that the crash has
OL,8,Fbeen the subject of "extensive
OL,9,Finvestigations", and that the CJC has
OL,10,Fnot "raised any information even
OL,11,Farguably capable of reviving any
OL,12,Finvestigative obligation".
OL,14,FHe also said that the Boeing
OL,15,Flitigation was "not relevant to the
OL,16,Fcrash" and that the CJC's case was
OL,17,Fbased on "vague assertions" about the
OL,18,Fhelicopter's airworthiness, without
OL,19,Fexplaining why the legal challenge had
OL,20,Fnot been brought sooner.
OL,26,@pD@UOUqD@OO]rD@EOUtD@YO]wD@POUxD@FO]yD@
OL,26,AJOUyD@[O]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}           G10/12
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,419,410,140,120,000,100
PN,41811
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F418A1784211519
OL,3,CLegal challenge over 1994 Chinook
OL,4,Ccrash should continue, High Court told
OL,6,FHe added: "The claimant suggests that
OL,7,Ffurther investigation of the crash
OL,8,Fcircumstances is still possible today.
OL,10,F"Yet given the paucity of evidence and
OL,11,Fthe passage of time, it is unlikely
OL,12,Fthat further meaningful investigation
OL,13,Fis possible, or that further
OL,14,Finvestigation would serve a practical
OL,15,Fpurpose."
OL,17,FHe continued: "The claimant
OL,18,Funderstandably wants to bring the full
OL,19,Ffacts to light.
OL,26,@nD@KOUrD@AOUwD@IO]yD@OOU
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}           G11/12
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,419,410,140,120,000,100
PN,41812
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F418A1784211519
OL,3,CLegal challenge over 1994 Chinook
OL,4,Ccrash should continue, High Court told
OL,6,F"However, that aspiration must be
OL,7,Fconsidered in view of the evidential
OL,8,Flimitations, the civil claims that
OL,9,Fhave been resolved, the lessons that
OL,10,Fhave been learned and the transformed
OL,11,Foperational context."
OL,13,FThe hearing before Mr Justice Butcher
OL,14,Fis due to conclude later on Tuesday.
